snippet: Fighting in eastern Ukraine left at least nine Ukrainian soldiers dead and 13 wounded on Friday, Ukrainian officials said.
abstract: Clashes in eastern Ukraine leave at least nine Ukrainian soldiers dead and wound 13 as government troops press their offensive against pro-Russian fighters.
lead_paragraph: Fighting in eastern Ukraine left at least nine Ukrainian soldiers dead and 13 wounded on Friday, Ukrainian officials said.

headline.main: Ukraine: Troops in Deadly Clash With Separatists
